  "body": "With a mist node that is mining and connected to 2 peers, the RCP methods `eth_listening` and `eth_mining` always return False.\n\nRequest:\n\n```\n{'params': None, 'jsonrpc': '2.0', 'id': '54eab6cd-b22b-4328-9fa2-ba56f4ddea0a', 'method': 'eth_listening'}\n```\n\nReponse:\n\n```\n{u'jsonrpc': u'2.0', u'id': u'54eab6cd-b22b-4328-9fa2-ba56f4ddea0a', u'result': False}\n```\n\nexpected: result = True\n\nRequest:\n\n```\n{'params': None, 'jsonrpc': '2.0', 'id': '33a739cf-0f31-47af-b42e-52f5871c0cc0', 'method': 'eth_mining'}\n```\n\nResponse:\n\n```\n{u'jsonrpc': u'2.0', u'id': u'33a739cf-0f31-47af-b42e-52f5871c0cc0', u'result': False}\n```\n\nexpected: result = True\n",
